name: WeddingBell
0:
”Alexa, open Wedding Bell”
”What day is the wedding?”
”I forgot the social media rules”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: wedding bell
des: Wedding Bell is the leading wedding communication assistant for brides and grooms. It's fully customizable, with your own voice, to keep your friends, family, and guests informed of all your wedding day specifics as well as share intimate details of events leading up to your big day!
